igins of Life</p><p class="sc-c-metadata__synopsis gs-u-hidden gel-brevier gs-u-mt- gs-u-mb">Melvyn Bragg and guests discuss when and how life on earth originated.</p><ul class="gs-o-list-inline gs-o-list-inline--divided"><li class="sc-c-metadata__duration gs-u-mt- gel-brevier" aria-label="duration: 45 mins">45 mins</li></ul></div></div></a></div></li><li class="sc-o-faux-wrap-end" style="width:0" aria-hidden="true"> </li></ul></div></div><div class="sc-c-carousel__blind sc-c-carousel__blind--left sc-o-island__point sc-o-island__point--tl"></div><div class="sc-c-carousel__blind sc-c-carousel__blind--right sc-o-island__point sc-o-island__point--tr"></div></div></div></section><div class="sc-c-navigation-footer gs-u-box-size gs-u-pv gs-u-pv+@m gel-wrap play-u-nav-footer-spacing"><ul class="sc-c-navigation-footer__languages sc-o-piped gel-1/1@xs gel-1/3@l gs-u-display-inline-block gs-u-align-top"><li class="gs-u-display-inline-block gs-u-mb-" lang="cy"><a class="sc-o-link sc-o-link--secondary gel-brevier-bold" data-bypassmodal="true" href="/sounds/language/cy"><span class="sc-o-link__text">Cymraeg</span></a></li><li class="gs-u-display-inline-block gs-u-mb-" lang="ga"><a class="sc-o-link sc-o-link--secondary gel-brevier-bold" data-bypassmodal="true" href="/sounds/language/ga"><span class="sc-o-link__text">Gaeilge</span></a></li><li class="gs-u-display-inline-block gs-u-mb-" lang="gd"><a class="sc-o-link sc-o-link--secondary gel-brevier-bold" data-bypassmodal="true" href="/sounds/language/gd"><span class="sc-o-link__text">Gàidhlig</span></a></li></ul><ul class="sc-c-navigation-footer__links sc-o-piped gel-1/1@xs gel-2/3@l gs-u-display-inline-block gs-u-mt+ gs-u-mt0@l gs-u-align-top"><li class="gs-u-display-inline-block gs-u-mb-"><a class="sc-o-link sc-o-link--secondary gel-brevier-bold" href="https://bbc.co.uk/sounds/help"><span class="sc-o-link__text">BBC Sounds Help</span></a></li><li class="gs-u-display-inline-block gs-u-mb-"><a class="sc-o-link sc-o-link--secondary 